Welcome
/$
$
/$
$
Located in the rolling hills of central Florida is a quite 55+ RV Resort that is the best kept secret we know. All residence and renters must be at least 40 years of age. We only have 154 sites for motor homes, 5th wheels, and 21+ foot trailers and park model homes. Most lots are 40' x 60' with all lots owned by members of the association. Many lots are available for rent or for sale. Come and look at a place that is warm and friendly with all the amenities you could ask for. Enjoy the tennis and pickleball courts, take a dip in the solar heated pool, take part in the many events that fill the calendar each week.
​
​
/$
$
We can be found on US Highway 27 just north of Clemont, FL. The rolling terrain, with a variety of palm trees and northern pines makes the landscaping very inviting.
Come enjoy central Florida, with access to the many exciting Disney venues and fantastic shopping. You will not be disappointed.
​
Disney World                             30 minutes
Universal Studios                      30 minutes
Sea World                                   35 minutes
Orlando Intl. Airport                  40 minutes
Sanford Intl. Airport                  1.0 hours
Daytona Beach                          1.5 hours
Tampa/Clearwater                     1.5 hours
South Lake Hospital                 15 minutes
Walmart                                      16 minutes
Publix Super Market                  11
minutes
Lowes                                         14 minutes
